Uxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BA%A1i-ng%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-thi%E1%BB%81n/poem-LvAgfE08bW_GHmspFhIapQ">Tại ngục vịnh thiền - 在獄詠蟬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-T%C3%A2n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-jvbfrjspi2Y6S8b3jeqzpA">Lạc Tân Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/Thi%C3%AAn-ni%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%A1ch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-c%E1%BB%95-nh%C3%A2n-tung/poem-p5CiCdUSZM094mZ7SNas8Q">Thiên niên thạch thượng cổ nhân tung - 千年石上古人蹤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%C3%A2n/Ti%C3%AAn-tr%C3%A0-thu%E1%BB%B7-k%C3%BD/poem-8WwuSop69rG9-aoxa8C2nQ">Tiên trà thuỷ ký - 煎茶水記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%C3%A2n/author-MfG9Dcv0CtbGpIaXvmxDnA">Trương Hựu Tân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
